description: Roast Calculator will let you know how long to cook your meat for in minutes. Useful when your hands a full and you need to get that roast cooking! Knows about Beef, Lamb, Pork and Chicken, and can understand kilos and pounds.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask Roast Calculator how long for one and a half pounds of beef
Alexa Ask Roast Calculator how long should I cook a one point five kilo piece of lamb
name: RoastCalculator
shortDescription: Roast Calculator will let you know how long to cook your meat for in minutes.
